- ğŸ¯ Smart Auto-Selection
- ğŸ“ˆ Built-in Insights
- ğŸ¨ Beautiful Themes
- ğŸ” One-Line EDA
- ğŸ“Š Statistical Annotations
- ğŸš€ Zero Configuration

